::Battera::

she flew after him for a few yards firing her optic lazars at him.  
She turned and flew back to Rex and Firearm.  She looked at them both 
and smiled.  "Well, if all the excitement is over with, I'll just go 
to my quarters now."  she transformed into bot mode and walked down 
the hallway.  She didn't give them time to speak to her, for she was 
afraid of what they might say.  She walked quickly to her room and 
closed the door behind her. She was afraid they might yell at her.
